hopobject.body: I'd like to pay this cheque in, please de.nutrend-supplements.com Prevention of low-risk prostate cancer offers a complementary strategy to early detection. The PCPT addressed the issue by randomizing almost 19,000 healthy, cancer-free men ≥55 to daily finasteride or placebo for 7 years. Participants had regular follow-up visits that included PSA testing and digital rectal exam, and biopsies were performed as indicated by the trial protocol.
